00:57:56,139 --> 00:57:58,440
   I don't want a new doll.

637
00:57:58,508 --> 00:58:00,042
            [slap]

638
00:58:00,109 --> 00:58:02,344
         I want Lily!

639
00:58:02,412 --> 00:58:04,980
            Claire!

640
00:58:05,048 --> 00:58:09,718
  Why do you always hurt me,
          Mommy? Why?

641
00:58:09,786 --> 00:58:11,687
          Oh, my God.

642
00:58:18,361 --> 00:58:20,295
 Okay, let's see what we got.

643
00:58:20,363 --> 00:58:21,930
           Ophelia?

644
00:58:21,998 --> 00:58:23,732
  Would you like me to start
       with the abdomen?

645
00:58:23,800 --> 00:58:25,601
         Sounds good.

646
00:59:02,572 --> 00:59:04,773
   Want me to check it out?

647
00:59:04,841 --> 00:59:08,310
       No, no, I'll go.
Call maintenance and stay here.

648
00:59:39,542 --> 00:59:41,376
         Hmm. Strange.

649
00:59:42,812 --> 00:59:45,213
            Hello?

650
00:59:45,281 --> 00:59:47,349
    Is there someone there?

651
01:00:19,215 --> 01:00:21,049
  We need to get out of here.

652
01:00:24,187 --> 01:00:25,520
           Ophelia?

653
01:00:29,425 --> 01:00:30,726
           Ophelia?

654
01:00:46,909 --> 01:00:49,244
           [screams]

