01:00:56,085 --> 01:00:57,886
There's Daddy's little princess.

656
01:00:59,355 --> 01:01:01,123
     I know what you want.

657
01:01:01,190 --> 01:01:04,359
    Daddy's world-famous...

658
01:01:04,427 --> 01:01:06,094
          flapjacks.

659
01:01:10,800 --> 01:01:13,268
          - Morning.
          - Morning.

660
01:01:13,336 --> 01:01:15,904
  Breakfast is almost ready.
    Can you get the juice?

661
01:01:15,972 --> 01:01:16,872
          Yeah, sure.

