         <i> How, Claire?</i>

684
01:02:13,396 --> 01:02:15,397
    <i> How did she hurt you?</i>

685
01:02:17,834 --> 01:02:20,435
    <i> I was in the kitchen,</i>

686
01:02:20,503 --> 01:02:23,839
    <i> and I spilled my milk,</i>

687
01:02:23,906 --> 01:02:27,142
        <i> and she just--</i>
<i> she just finished cleaning up,</i>

688
01:02:27,210 --> 01:02:28,510
            <i> and...</i>

689
01:02:31,013 --> 01:02:32,748
       <i> and she got mad.</i>

690
01:02:34,884 --> 01:02:38,320
   <i> Claire, I'm going to go</i>
   <i> and get a special report</i>

691
01:02:38,387 --> 01:02:40,655
  <i> so I can write this down.</i>

692
