I'm in the middle of something.

694
01:03:07,984 --> 01:03:11,453
 I know, but someone left this
      in the front door.

695
01:03:11,521 --> 01:03:14,689
  It's the Simon girl's doll,
           isn't it?

696
01:03:14,757 --> 01:03:16,558
        - Who left it?
         - Don't know.

697
01:03:16,626 --> 01:03:19,261
  I went to put the mail out,
and it was just sitting there.

698
01:03:21,030 --> 01:03:24,299
     Just keep it up front
         for me, okay?

699
01:03:24,367 --> 01:03:25,333
             Sure.

700
01:03:25,401 --> 01:03:26,868
  And there's another thing.

701
01:03:26,936 --> 01:03:28,770
  It's about Zachary Orcutt.

702
01:03:40,383 --> 01:03:42,150
    That's a lot of blood.

703
01:03:42,218 --> 01:03:43,652
  Yeah, looks like our victim
      was killed up here,

704
01:03:43,719 --> 01:03:45,887
then dragged down to the desk.

705
01:03:48,391 --> 01:03:50,192
        Can I help you?

706
01:03:50,259 --> 01:03:51,760
       Yeah, I'm sorry,

707
01:03:51,828 --> 01:03:54,029
    but Professor Carranza
     was a friend of mine,

708
01:03:54,096 --> 01:03:57,699
       and I'm wondering
  if anyone has found a doll.

709
01:03:57,767 --> 01:03:59,501
            A doll?

710
01:03:59,569 --> 01:04:01,536
 Yeah, I came by, I dropped it
    off with her yesterday.

711
01:04:01,604 --> 01:04:02,704
     She was looking into
       something for me.

712
01:04:02,772 --> 01:04:04,773
 I'm gonna need you to leave.

713
01:04:04,841 --> 01:04:07,008
  There's a detective outside
 that'll take your statement.

714
01:04:07,076 --> 01:04:09,344
     Danny, can you please
    escort this woman out?

715
01:04:09,412 --> 01:04:12,013
Okay, but it's really important
   that you find this doll.

716
01:04:12,081 --> 01:04:13,782
 - I need you to come with me.
         - Yeah, but--

717
01:04:13,850 --> 01:04:15,984
    - Get her out of here.
      - Yeah, okay, I'm--

718
01:04:16,052 --> 01:04:17,652
        Right this way.

719
01:04:17,720 --> 01:04:19,321
           - Sorry.
    - [cell phone ringing]

720
01:04:19,388 --> 01:04:23,024
   Anyway, they dragged her
      from here to there.

721
01:04:23,092 --> 01:04:24,192
            Right.
      And down the steps.

722
01:04:27,096 --> 01:04:28,630
            Hello?

723
01:04:28,698 --> 01:04:30,298
 I really need to talk to you
         about Claire.

724
01:04:30,366 --> 01:04:32,167
  How soon can you get here?

725
01:04:32,235 --> 01:04:36,404
 Halfway to the city is gonna
 be like another hour or two.

726
01:04:36,472 --> 01:04:39,107
    I know you went to see
        Zachary Orcutt.

727
01:04:39,175 --> 01:04:42,444
   <i> You know I evaluated him</i>
 <i> for the court five years ago</i>

728
01:04:42,511 --> 01:04:44,512
<i> after he murdered his family.</i>

729
01:04:44,580 --> 01:04:46,248
       Okay. Why are you
       telling me this?

730
01:04:46,315 --> 01:04:48,683
         Shortly after
      you spoke with him,

731
01:04:48,751 --> 01:04:51,152
        Zachary Orcutt
   disappeared from his ward

732
01:04:51,220 --> 01:04:53,688
 <i> and hasn't been seen since.</i>

733
01:04:56,125 --> 01:04:59,728
      Are you telling me
   that Claire is in danger?

734
01:04:59,795 --> 01:05:01,963
        <i> Just get here</i>
     <i> as soon as you can.</i>

735
01:05:04,500 --> 01:05:07,035
      Jane, I need you to
     reschedule my next--

736
01:05:18,347 --> 01:05:19,915
          [clinking]

